#: ../../../ScalableStaticAnalysisFramework/user-docs/SummaryExtraction.rst:3
msgid "Summary Extraction"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../ScalableStaticAnalysisFramework/user-docs/SummaryExtraction.rst:5
msgid ""
"The framework is rapidly evolving. The documentation might be out-of-sync "
"with the implementation. The purpose of this documentation is to give "
"context for upcoming reviews."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../ScalableStaticAnalysisFramework/user-docs/SummaryExtraction.rst:10
msgid "Command-line interface"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../ScalableStaticAnalysisFramework/user-docs/SummaryExtraction.rst:12
msgid "Two flags control summary extraction:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../ScalableStaticAnalysisFramework/user-docs/SummaryExtraction.rst:14
msgid ""
"``--ssaf-extract-summaries=<name1>,<name2>,...``: Comma-separated list of "
"summary extractor names to enable."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../ScalableStaticAnalysisFramework/user-docs/SummaryExtraction.rst:15
msgid ""
"``--ssaf-tu-summary-file=<path>.<format>``: Output file for the extracted "
"summaries. The file extension selects the serialization format (e.g. ``."
"json``)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../ScalableStaticAnalysisFramework/user-docs/SummaryExtraction.rst:16
msgid "``--ssaf-list-extractors``: List the available summary extractors."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../ScalableStaticAnalysisFramework/user-docs/SummaryExtraction.rst:17
msgid "``--ssaf-list-formats``: List the available serialization formats."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../ScalableStaticAnalysisFramework/user-docs/SummaryExtraction.rst:19
msgid "Example invocation:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../ScalableStaticAnalysisFramework/user-docs/SummaryExtraction.rst:30
msgid "Diagnostics"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../ScalableStaticAnalysisFramework/user-docs/SummaryExtraction.rst:32
msgid ""
"In case the ``--ssaf-*`` flags are used incorrectly, or some extractor fails "
"to implement the desired serialization format or just happens to have an "
"error, then the error is forwarded as a ``scalable-static-analysis-"
"framework`` error. These errors can be downgraded into warnings using ``-Wno-"
"error=scalable-static-analysis-framework``. These errors can be completely "
"suppressed using ``-Wno-scalable-static-analysis-framework``."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../ScalableStaticAnalysisFramework/user-docs/SummaryExtraction.rst:37
msgid ""
"See the `diagnostic flags <https://clang.llvm.org/docs/DiagnosticsReference."
"html#wscalable-static-analysis-framework>`_ for the full list of diagnostics "
"controlled by ``-Wscalable-static-analysis-framework``."
msgstr ""
